name: MUSKOLOGY | New Pop-Gogh #1
description:
MUSKOLOGY - is a Musk knowledge. These days, when it comes to Musk, I made such a work by blending the first few things that come to mind with my own illustration style ''New Pop-Gogh''

The New Pop-Gogh collection is an NFT art collection in which the artist discovers himself and creates new compositions using the harmonies of different colors, with a somewhat impressionist, somewhat pop-art approach.

Dimensions: 3000x3000

Ahmet Oğuzhan Akkök ''Uzokhan''
